<!doctype html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/dashboard-new.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/custom.css">

  <title>Info - Soft Botz</title>

  <style>
    main.dashboard-grid { margin-top: 24px; }

    .info-hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 10px 40px;
    }

    .info-hero h2 {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg,#8b5cf6,#a78bfa);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .info-hero p {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 14px auto 0;
      color: #9aa0a6;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .info-card {
      position: relative;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.045);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 28px;
      transition: all .4s ease;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .info-card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(139,92,246,.25), transparent 60%);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity .4s ease;
    }

    .info-card:hover::after {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .info-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(130,90,255,.35);
    }

    .info-icon {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg,#8b5cf6,#a78bfa);
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(139,92,246,.5);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .info-card h4 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .info-card p {
      font-size: .95rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #9aa0a6;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .info-card ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .info-card ul li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      font-size: .9rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .info-card ul li i {
      color: #8b5cf6;
      min-width: 18px;
      margin-top: 3px;
    }

    body.light .info-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #111827;
    }

    body.light .info-card p,
    body.light .info-card ul li {
      color: #374151;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
<div id="tsparticles"></div>
<div class="container">

<nav>
  <div class="nav-left"><h3>Soft Botz</h3></div>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <a href="/dashboard" title="Dashboard"><i class="fas fa-th-large"></i> <span>Dashboard</span></a>
                <a href="/custom" title="Custom Bot"><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> <span>Custom Bot</span></a>
                <a href="/donasi" title="Berdonasi"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i> <span>Donasi</span></a>
                <a href="/langganan" title="Langganan"><i class="fas fa-gem"></i> <span>Berlangganan</span></a>
                <a href="/info" class="active" title="Informasi"><i class="fas fa-circle-info"></i> <span>Info</span></a>
    <button id="theme-toggle" class="theme-toggle-btn">
      <i class="fas fa-moon"></i><i class="fas fa-sun"></i>
    </button>
    <div class="profile-dropdown">
              <img src="media/pp.jpg" alt="Avatar" class="avatar">
              <div class="dropdown-content">
                  <a href="/profile"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> Profile</a>
                  <a href="/report"><i class="fas fa-bug"></i> Report Bug/Error</a>
                  <a href="/logout"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Log out</a>
              </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<main class="dashboard-grid">
<div class="panel full-width-panel">

<div class="info-hero">
  <h2>Soft Botz Platform</h2>
  <p>
    Soft Botz adalah platform jadibot WhatsApp berbasis web yang dirancang
    untuk memudahkan siapa pun, dari pemula hingga advanced user, dalam membuat, mengelola, dan mengoptimalkan bot WhatsApp secara efisien.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="info-grid">

<div class="info-card">
  <div class="info-icon"><i class="bi bi-whatsapp"></i></div>
  <h4>Platform JadiBot WhatsApp</h4>
  <p>
    Soft Botz menyediakan sistem jadibot WhatsApp berbasis dashboard
    dengan kontrol penuh tanpa perlu setup rumit.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Siap pakai & mudah dikonfigurasi</li>
    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Cocok untuk personal & komunitas</li>
    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Mendukung penggunaan jangka panjang</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
  <div class="info-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
  <h4>Keamanan Website & Data</h4>
  <p>
    Keamanan menjadi prioritas utama. Sistem dilindungi dengan validasi,
    pembatasan akses, dan monitoring berkala.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><i class="bi bi-lock-fill"></i> Proteksi data user</li>
    <li><i class="bi bi-bug-fill"></i> Laporan bug langsung ke admin</li>
    <li><i class="bi bi-eye-fill"></i> Monitoring aktivitas sistem</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
  <div class="info-icon"><i class="bi bi-brush"></i></div>
  <h4>UI / UX Ramah Pengguna</h4>
  <p>
    Tampilan dibuat simpel, bersih, dan konsisten agar
    user awam tidak bingung saat menggunakan fitur.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i> Layout jelas & terstruktur</li>
    <li><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Mudah dibaca & dipahami</li>
    <li><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> Responsive semua device</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
  <div class="info-icon"><i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i></div>
  <h4>Sistem Custom Fleksibel</h4>
  <p>
    Semua pengaturan utama bot dapat dikontrol langsung
    melalui dashboard tanpa coding manual.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><i class="fas fa-robot"></i> Nama bot & owner</li>
    <li><i class="fas fa-image"></i> Thumbnail & sticker</li>
    <li><i class="fas fa-gauge"></i> Limit & fitur bot</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
  <div class="info-icon"><i class="bi bi-lightning-charge"></i></div>
  <h4>Performa & Stabilitas</h4>
  <p>
    Sistem dirancang agar tetap ringan, cepat,
    dan stabil walau digunakan terus-menerus.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Optimasi performa</li>
    <li><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Minim downtime</li>
    <li><i class="fas fa-server"></i> Server terkontrol</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
  <div class="info-icon"><i class="fas fa-headset"></i></div>
  <h4>Dukungan & Pengembangan</h4>
  <p>
    Soft Botz terus dikembangkan dengan fitur baru
    dan admin siap membantu jika terjadi kendala.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> Support via WhatsApp</li>
    <li><i class="fas fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i> Support via chat AI di dashboard</li>
    <li><i class="fas fa-wrench"></i> Update berkala</li>
    <li><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Fitur terus berkembang</li>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</main>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tsparticles-bundle@2.12.0/tsparticles.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/custom.js"></script>
</body>
</html>